videos.description: Solomon Young throws down the dunk off the sweet dish from Monte Morris.
videos.headline: ISU's Young throws down the dunk

videos.description: Solomon Young unintentionally steals an alley-oop from his teammate and throws it down himself.
videos.headline: ISU's Young steals alley-oop from his own teammate

videos.description: ISU Head Coach Steve Prohm says ball movement as well as good shots have helped ISU build their lead at the half.
videos.headline: Steve Prohm says ball movement has the been the key for ISU in the 1st half

videos.description: When asked how his game compares to OKC's Russell Westbrook, Monte Morris praises the Thunder guard.

videos.description: Monte Morris' 15 points and 5 assists, Solomon Young's 18 points, lead the Cyclones to a 87-79 win over the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Monte Morris and Solomon Young lead ISU past K-State
